uNET module¶

uNET.importModules(logger)[source]¶

import and execute required modules

This function is used for importing all the modules as defined in the ../config/modules.json file and executing the main function within it if present. In error, it fails gracefully …

Parameters:logger ({logging.Logger}) – logger module for logging information
uNET.main(logger)[source]¶

main program

This is the place where the entire program is going to be generated.
